        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Greedy/mission_raccoon/scene_raccoon_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 89c446da-527e-4bd1-b707-6f78949ffd38).Image",
        "Description": "The Milton-Fitzpatrick Bank has hired us to take care of some of their underperforming employees. The bank would fire them, but that would mean paying severence, and after being bought out by Valve the ICA now offers discounts during the summer season, making us the more cost efficient option. The targets can all be found on the bottom floor of the bank near the vault, and the client would prefer that you dispatch them discreetly.  This, however, is optional. Good luck, and earn your paycheck.",
